<h1 class="hero-h">2026 Fractional Executive <em>Pricing Report.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">The definitive 2026 pricing reference for fractional CMO, CRO, CFO, COO, CHRO, and CTO engagements. Retainer ranges, hourly rates, what drives the number up and down, and how each role stacks against the full-time alternative. Decision-ready and citable.</p>
